{"data":[{"id":559545250,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2de5a04eb109b762e37736fbed8e5016","url_token":"ka-mu","name":"咖木","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/444f88095c8c53619c4889a86dc07ccd_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/444f88095c8c53619c4889a86dc07ccd_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2de5a04eb109b762e37736fbed8e5016","user_type":"people","headline":"萌新炼丹学徒","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559545250","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545737703,"updated_time":1545738443,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1130,"content":"\u003cp\u003e问：如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e答：能。请致电清华大学招生办\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e联系方式\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2\u003e电话：010－62770334，62782051\u003cbr\u003e传真：010－62782061\u003cbr\u003e邮编：100084 \u003cbr\u003e地址：北京市海淀区清华园1号清华大学招生办 \u003cbr\u003eEmail：zsb@tsinghua.edu.cn\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外清华招生办不使用知乎办公，在知乎上发表的文章也不会作为是否录取的标准。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557748781,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8b2af7455bbb2f96d6866399a5e7b88d","url_token":"bigdick-50","name":"bigDick","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4bee500fb14821b64995c0a54d2e06f3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4bee500fb14821b64995c0a54d2e06f3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8b2af7455bbb2f96d6866399a5e7b88d","user_type":"people","headline":"turnon","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557748781","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545523549,"updated_time":1545523549,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1048,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你应该是高中生吧。。你问反了。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你这个问题等于是在问：  我们省会。有一家好出名的拳馆  请问  我拿到了四大金腰带，拳馆会收我入籍吗。。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你就是抱着混一个好学历的心态，但是你可能不知道 你 证明哥德巴赫的猜想。 你可以去全球任何一所大学教书了。。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不知道你是不是想独辟畦径，高中几年时间博一下 证出来就清华。。。你要知道，全球那么多优秀的数学家——还不是大学生，都搞不定。如果你有这想法，你还不如想一下 你拿诺贝尔物理学奖你会选哈佛牛津加州理工哪个大学去当教授来的好   因为这个比证明哥德巴赫的猜想要简单。。。。的多。。。。        清华还配不上你。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561087604,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19","url_token":"mo-he-yao-yao","name":"Vayne嫒","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19","user_type":"people","headline":"医学生","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561087604","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545915196,"updated_time":1545915196,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":480,"content":"\u003cp\u003e孩子，希望你能看见我这条回答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我没有任何质疑你能力的意思，但是我清楚地知道，要证明哥德巴赫猜想，其中所涉及的知识绝非你在高中奥赛班能够学到的。而你讲证明发表在知乎这种非专业性平台的举措，表明你对真正的数学领域知之甚少。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我并不阻止你发表，但我诚恳地希望你经过这一次尝试后，可以将目光回归到脚下的路。你对应试教育的意见是不成熟的，似乎你认为高考对于你这样在某一学科方面的天才非常不公平。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想告诉你，高中并没有在培养你。它不过是在检验你的学习能力罢了。当你通过高考证明了你的学习能力之后，真正的培养资源才会向你打开。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那些考不上大学的人宣称读书无用，学的数学一辈子都用不上，其实是因为他们证明自己的学习能力失败了，于是他们被淘汰进入与知识培养无关的工作领域。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在大学，你会发现一切都重新开始，在这里才是真正的学习和培养，学到的都是与职业密不可分的东西。在高中，真的只是证明你自己的学习能力，从而说服大学将资源投资给你罢了。而学习能力，是不分学科的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望你可以想通，不要在不正确的道路上执迷。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559674518,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"958556bd18d98edd9e9324d78ea85f69","url_token":"he-yin-67-55","name":"呵鹅河的何","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/82bb399229e0bc91f43ce7f58ff99f4e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/82bb399229e0bc91f43ce7f58ff99f4e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/958556bd18d98edd9e9324d78ea85f69","user_type":"people","headline":"职业经理人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559674518","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545750345,"updated_time":1545750345,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1359,"content":"\u003cp\u003e刘路，中南大学数学系，大三时独立解决了西塔潘猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e直接聘为教授，直博，留校。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刘路和我一栋宿舍，住在6楼，成名后偶尔还会在学校遇到…基本是明星待遇。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561746835,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","url_token":"lian-ke-30","name":"假语","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","user_type":"people","headline":"十分冷淡存知己，一曲微茫度此生。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561746835","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995761,"updated_time":1546003532,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":113,"content":"\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲失败了，是哗众取宠的小丑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲成功了，那就是睥睨四顾的成功人士了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你看，刚刚骂人家骂得正爽，觉得这种脑子的人这辈子都不能成功，可是一转眼，他现在就已经从一个民科升华成了一个移动的流量大v了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然他现在看起来还是个民科也或者高一新生。但是你看看别人关注数量，很多人拿赞同数量举例。其实他们根本不明白赞同和关注的区别\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e再看看别人的回答流量，虽然不知道他本意是否是炒作。但是这19k的关注。和浑身上下自带的流量，加上知乎这个平台对于高关注用户的偏爱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且，19k的关注远远不是终点，现在热度还没有停止呢，并且知乎也在为了热度恶意的引导着流量\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人不相信我，那我便举几个例子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e比如这位叶青大v，他积攒了几年的粉丝为18k。用了几年的时间，而最开始他还仅仅只是一个不知名用户的时候，就依靠阅读流量获得了极多邀请合作，以及在答案里面植入广告的邀请。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而我们的高中生，证明大v。却坐拥19k的活跃用户关注，其中还包括不少大v。也就是他最少也足以在短期内达到叶青大v层次的水平，一些说只值几百块钱的朋友，我只能说你对于流量变现太没有概念了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这个问题的流量更是可怕至极，如图所示。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前来说他的帐号价值已经上了六位数以上了。这是什么意思。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也就是人家选择最愚蠢的变现方式，把这个账号卖了。也足以变现数十万了，至于其他的各种变现方式，最简单就是成为一个大v开一个公众号。流量变现。足以让他在高中就月入五位数，如果经营得好。足以让自己年收入比得上一个小资家庭的年收入了，高考加分也无非请人代笔发表一篇简简单单的论文再背上一背。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在这个帐号那怕是拿来给我这种不怎么熟悉知乎各种潜规则的人来运用，也足以达成月入过万这种小目标，而给某些人能够产生的流量更是难以直接计算。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想想人家高一就能赚数十万，想出如此的完美炒作方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕是哗众取宠。人家也已经成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个案例足以位列知乎最近三年成功的钓鱼案例。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们对于钓鱼者的冷嘲热讽也无非是在赠送流量，为他的变现添砖加瓦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也不知道是有预谋的炒作还是天意如此。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只知道，他确实成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个成功者，还是值得我献上一点敬意的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕，靠的只是运气\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559531221,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a36d37d00a00c411b28e3c392116eeac","url_token":"EsseEstPercipi","name":"EricTseng","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/0d372c83a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/0d372c83a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a36d37d00a00c411b28e3c392116eeac","user_type":"people","headline":"不能接受其最差的一面，就不配拥有其最好的一面。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559531221","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545736254,"updated_time":1545736701,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":316,"content":"把原文稿打印好，以各种邮寄方式邮寄一份给自己，收到之后不要拆封。\u003cbr\u003e当然还有各种电子邮箱自己发给自己等等。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e做好了时间戳，能证明确实是你最先想到的。保证别人无法窃取你的“果实”（起码在国内保证这一点）\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e只有实质存在的证据，才能在法律上证明这是你的成果。\u003cbr\u003e不然别到时候冒出来什么人，说他半年前就做出来的东西你给偷了啥的。\u003cbr\u003e万一你俩都没证据咋整。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e然后明天白天把邮寄的事都弄好了，明天晚上就把你的证明发出来。\u003cbr\u003e【后天】联系知乎把这个问题关闭。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e算上今天，最多忍这个问题3天，忍不了多存在一天。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003ep.s.别忘了提前照两张喝营养品的照片放网上。什么忘不了3a脑营养胶丸啥的。代言起来方便，有提前做铺垫的话，衔接起来比较自然。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559485297,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559485297","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545731228,"updated_time":1545731228,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":236,"content":"\u003cp\u003e“那！当然可以啦！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“北大请你来当教授！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——李伟固\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559821648,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"59f511de84b683595d545fe3dafa93e6","url_token":"gao-shi-ping-90","name":"天涯比邻星","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c9c933bdea3fe7a03f26e5e826a9ef7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c9c933bdea3fe7a03f26e5e826a9ef7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/59f511de84b683595d545fe3dafa93e6","user_type":"people","headline":"间歇性踌躇满志，持续性混吃等死。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559821648","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-067141865ef4eaf47ec8a5280866b6e3_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545785825,"updated_time":1545785825,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":266,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主你好：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0233d6bed4b136e65b5630ef29743bce_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"476\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a5f4d2f8f06464a0e43bde7674c877cb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"476\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0233d6bed4b136e65b5630ef29743bce_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='476'%20height='338'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"476\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a5f4d2f8f06464a0e43bde7674c877cb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"476\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0233d6bed4b136e65b5630ef29743bce_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0233d6bed4b136e65b5630ef29743bce_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是我多年前设计好的永动机，劳烦题主19年1月1日顺便帮我一并发表了吧～（逃）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559491957,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f894828b18266a9e1e94bb7b29f2f9b6","url_token":"enoch-zhao","name":"Enoch Zhao","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f894828b18266a9e1e94bb7b29f2f9b6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559491957","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545731906,"updated_time":1545731906,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1559,"content":"\u003cp\u003e首先，就像大家说的如果真的证明了，上清华北大肯定不成问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其次，虽然被证明的可能性不高，但在没有看到证明过程之前最好不要下结论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，我的建议是，如果证明挂出来之后，被证明是错误的，希望题主可以认识到问题所在并学习相关知识，以后可以继续挑战这个问题，而不要坚持己见，拒不承认错误，这样真的就是民科了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后希望题主的证明是正确的。如果是正确的，直接拿菲尔兹奖，这样的大人物也不会和我们这些外行计较，如果是错误的，现在开始好好学习，考上一个靠谱的大学，即使不是清华北大，经过系统的学习也是可以取的一些研究成果的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560273018,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d625e057ba5c7fff539cd514b84f0329","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560273018","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545824653,"updated_time":1545824653,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":44,"content":"\u003cp\u003e在这个问题下为题主祝贺叫好的诸位忘了凡伟了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/59471035/answer/165656590\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1825018d44043bb90a9f094b49317a79_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2270\" data-image-height=\"1016\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如何评价凡伟提出的电荷不存在理论？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e立个flag，这题主要是能证明哥猜，我哈士奇的哈字换个部首。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560704522,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"89451b5e351a23ab21b2c9fcc6218ab9","url_token":"mu-yu-59-38","name":"木雨","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a8f60fac4f2dccc134ef51c3f2528aa3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a8f60fac4f2dccc134ef51c3f2528aa3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/89451b5e351a23ab21b2c9fcc6218ab9","user_type":"people","headline":"爱听故事的大儿童","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560704522","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545880686,"updated_time":1545887009,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":209,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e抽奖警告\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e抽奖警告\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e抽奖警告\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e一月一日，如果\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 成功证明出哥德巴赫猜想，我鼓掌，流泪，感慨有生之年的同时，做一点微小的贡献，文体两开花。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e抽奖内容：\u003c/b\u003e我将采用直播DOTA roll点的方式，在评论区抽一位朋友送出switch一台（附赠游戏：塞尔达传说，NBA 2k 18），\u003cb\u003e如果食言，甘受各类辱骂绝不还口\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e参与方式：关注我，\u003c/b\u003e点赞这条回答，并留言任意内容。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e才疏学浅，人微言轻，工薪小民，只能做这么多了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e原回答：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不知道题主是装睡还是真睡啊，所以下面的回答不针对个人，只针对这个问题本身……说到本身，我就想起了真假孙悟空本身和假身……中美……两开花……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e额，说秃噜嘴了不好意思。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e严肃说，一个高中生，别说能成功证明哥德巴赫猜想了，你哪怕没证明出来，但证明过程中充分展现了自己有证明哥德巴赫猜想的知识储备……你也能保送了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eso，1.1号，希望这个问题下99%的人能看不懂你的答案并真心说一句nb吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺便说一句，把这问题推上来，知乎挺坏的……\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559515191,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1f2b8e45afd14c6515dbeb39d5dd3bc2","url_token":"zhou-heng-yi-36","name":"紫蓝星逸","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-91c47177e551dca341ad057bb4cc0541_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-91c47177e551dca341ad057bb4cc0541_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1f2b8e45afd14c6515dbeb39d5dd3bc2","user_type":"people","headline":"退乎，只点赞，不回答","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559515191","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545734501,"updated_time":1545881253,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":131,"content":"\u003cp\u003e好的好的，我们都等着呢！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月1号是吧？没问题，31号晚上我一定熬到十二点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们这种“官科”都算不上的不敢乱评价您，估计到时候您的证明我这种高中数学都不行的人也看不懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那些水平高深的数学家又不会专门上知乎看您的文章，那可怎么办才好？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我真的是为题主感到非常的焦虑，不过\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e单纯论手法，题主比大多数民科都强哦\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一般民科创造奇迹以后都是立马发到网上然后光速打脸。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个小朋友故意拖个几天，挑个黄道吉日，还弄个高中生人设，喷又不能喷的过分，还能顺便涨粉。你看，人家粉丝都500＋\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e唉:-(，是我咸吃萝卜淡操心了。题主肯定有办法引起数学大V们的关注，嗯⊙∀⊙！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到哥德巴赫猜想，西游记里充满了各种难以置信的奇思妙想，明年由我带头，中美合资的3D西游记，就要开拍了，文体两开花，希望大家多多关注！\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在有点不爽了，昨天看到那个匿名老师的回答，原来已经变得很友善了。但是，昨天11点多，题主又发了一篇文章，申明自己的证明根本没有外传过。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在想知道，这个匿名的老师到底是不是真的？他的言辞为什么与题主不符合？是题主自己作，不承认证明有问题，还是这个匿名用户不存在，是某人假冒的？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e既然自称是题主的老师，说话还有理有据的，那按他的身份应该是题主的高中数学老师，为什么题主申明里用的是“那位老师”！我对这个称谓很感兴趣。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不是我黑暗，我现在怀疑是题主匿名回答，希望匿名用户或者题主出来解释解释？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559785440,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"29448cc28212a543bea56b9492f82e25","url_token":"morgancheng","name":"程墨Morgan","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/04d3c071d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/04d3c071d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/29448cc28212a543bea56b9492f82e25","user_type":"people","headline":"互联网研发老兵，微信公众号morgansays，《深入浅出React和Redux》作者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559785440","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545779269,"updated_time":1545779269,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":471,"content":"\u003cp\u003e肯定不会，如果高中生就证明了哥德巴赫猜想，那还清什么华什么北什么大？全世界任何一所大学你随便挑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而，醒醒，不要幻想着高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在中科院的附近，有段时间（也许现在还有）总能看到一些人在路边闲逛，眼神呆滞，看到有人路过，就递上去一个小条，上面三言两语几个公式“证明”了哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些人，就是被“证明哥德巴赫猜想就可以直接进高等学府”这种想法耽误的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560667253,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"242dd9f71ffc0da37adb60670312514f","url_token":"dong-tian-wen-35-51","name":"董天文","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d06eac6c33af85b5cc1848d76cfd6cf_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d06eac6c33af85b5cc1848d76cfd6cf_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/242dd9f71ffc0da37adb60670312514f","user_type":"people","headline":"数学建模多次最高奖得主/吹水指导","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560667253","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545878061,"updated_time":1545878061,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":68,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不玩知乎的我也来吃瓜了...\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559819473,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"be87b4e84adf198dfe85866e54e46560","url_token":"jian-jia-hai","name":"只是银枪暮雪","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dbb74aff616ca0f8600eda1da4af1642_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dbb74aff616ca0f8600eda1da4af1642_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/be87b4e84adf198dfe85866e54e46560","user_type":"people","headline":"基础数学","badge":[],"gen